author: Divya Rao
title: Photo: Kajol Wishes Her Gorgeous Sister Tanisha Mukerji For Her Birthday
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 4 . 2017 
Ex Bigg Boss contestant and actress Tanisha Mukerji just turned 35 and her doting sister Kajol took to Instagram to wish her for it. Take a look. A post shared by Kajol Devgan (@kajol) on Mar 2, 2017 at 8:35pm PST 
Awww! Happy Birthday, Tanisha. :) The birthday girl let us in on how she celebrated the big day. A post shared by Tanishaa Mukerji (@tanishaamukerji) on Mar 3, 2017 at 12:20am PST 
Fun fun fun!
